🚀 PROJOBHUB
A modern, full-featured job portal built with React, TypeScript, and Supabase — crafted by Krish Yadav. 🌟

📋 PROJECT OVERVIEW
ProJobHub connects job seekers with opportunities and empowers employers to post jobs effortlessly. Powered by cutting-edge technologies and a sleek, user-friendly design, it’s your go-to platform for career growth. 💼

🔐 AUTHENTICATION & USER MANAGEMENT

🔑 Supabase Auth: Secure sign-up and login system  
👤 User Profiles: Manage personal and professional details  
🚫 Protected Routes: Restrict access to authenticated features


💼 JOB MANAGEMENT

🔍 Job Browsing: Explore job listings with ease  
🎯 Advanced Filtering: Filter by role, location, salary, experience, and more  
🧾 Job Details Modal: Clean, intuitive UI (e.g., JobModal.tsx with smooth close button)  
➕ Job Posting: Seamless job creation for logged-in employers


💬 REAL-TIME MESSAGING

💬 Live Chat: Powered by Supabase Realtime for instant communication  
👥 Community Features: Connect with peers and recruiters


🎨 MODERN UI/UX

📱 Responsive Design: Flawless experience across all devices  
💫 Animations: Smooth transitions and hover effects  
🧊 Glassmorphism: Sleek, modern aesthetic  
🌌 Moving Background: Dynamic, engaging visuals  
🌗 Dark/Light Mode: Theme support with next-themes


🔍 SMART SEARCH & FILTERING

📝 Keyword Search: Find jobs by relevant terms  
📍 Location Filter: Remote, onsite, or hybrid options  
💰 Salary Range: Adjustable slider for budget preferences  
📈 Experience Level: From junior to senior roles  
⏳ Employment Type: Full-time, part-time, contract, or internship


🛠️ TECHNOLOGY STACK
⚛️ Frontend

React 18 + Hooks: Dynamic and interactive UI  
TypeScript: Type-safe development for reliability  
Vite ⚡: Lightning-fast build and dev tooling  
Tailwind CSS 🎨: Utility-first CSS for stunning designs  
shadcn/ui 🧩: Reusable, modern UI components

🔙 Backend & Database

Supabase: Backend-as-a-service for auth, storage, and real-time features 🔐  
PostgreSQL: Robust relational database 🗄️  
Row-Level Security (RLS): Secure data access 🛡️  
Real-time Subscriptions: Live updates for jobs and messages 🔔

🧰 Libraries

React Router DOM: Seamless client-side routing  
Tanstack React Query: Efficient data fetching and caching  
React Hook Form: Streamlined form handling  
Lucide React: Modern, customizable icons ✨  
Recharts: Interactive graphs and charts 📊


📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE
src/
├── 📁 components/
│   ├── 📁 ui/              # shadcn/ui components
│   ├── 📄 JobCard.tsx      # Job listing card
│   ├── 📄 JobList.tsx      # Job listing grid
│   ├── 📄 JobModal.tsx     # Job details modal
│   ├── 📄 JobSidebar.tsx   # Filter and search sidebar
├── 📁 pages/
│   ├── 📄 Index.tsx        # Home page
│   ├── 📄 Auth.tsx         # Authentication page
│   ├── 📄 Profile.tsx      # User profile management
│   ├── 📄 Messages.tsx     # Real-time messaging
│   ├── 📄 Hiring.tsx       # Employer job posting
├── 📁 hooks/
│   └── 📄 useAuth.tsx      # Custom auth hook
├── 📁 services/
│   └── 📄 jobsService.ts   # Job-related API logic
├── 📁 data/
│   └── 📄 jobs.ts          # Mock job data
└── 📁 integrations/
    └── 📁 supabase/        # Supabase client setup


🗄️ DATABASE SCHEMA

🧑 profiles: Stores user information  
💼 jobs: Manages job listings  
💬 messages: Powers the chat system

🔐 Security Features

Row-Level Security (RLS): Fine-grained access control  
Auto-profile Creation: Seamless user onboarding  
Real-time Updates: Live job and message syncing


🎯 CORE FUNCTIONALITY

🛠️ CRUD Operations: Create, read, update, and delete jobs  
📡 Real-time Updates: Instant job and message updates  
📱 Responsive UX: Smooth experience across devices  
🔁 Modern Loading States: Visual feedback for actions  
❌ Robust Error Handling: Graceful error management


📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN
Optimized for all screen sizes:  

📱 Mobile: 320px+  
💻 Tablets: 768px+  
🖥️ Desktops: 1024px+  
🖥️ Large Screens: 1440px+


🔧 CONFIGURATION

🛠️ Supabase Backend: Configured for auth, storage, and real-time  
🗃️ Database Migrations: Managed schema updates  
🛡️ Row-Level Security: Secure data access  
🔄 Real-time Subscriptions: Live data syncing  
🔐 Authentication Flow: Seamless sign-up and login


🎨 DESIGN SYSTEM

🎨 Gradient Color Scheme: Vibrant and modern  
🆎 Clean Typography: Readable and professional  
🧩 shadcn/ui Components: Consistent and reusable  
🌀 Smooth Transitions: Enhanced user interactions  
🔣 Lucide Icons: Featuring X, Bookmark, MapPin, and more


▶️ RUN THE PROJECT

Clone the repository:  
git clone https://github.com/krishyadav90/ProJobHub.git
cd ProJobHub


Install dependencies:  
npm install


Set up environment variables in .env:  
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key


Start the development server:  
npm run dev



Visit http://localhost:5173 to explore ProJobHub! 🌐

